<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
  <h1 style="color: #dc3545; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">
    Account Blocked
  </h1>
</div>

<div style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    Dear <strong><%= companyName || 'Seller' %></strong>,
  </p>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    We regret to inform you that your Canadian Bazaar seller account has been temporarily blocked.
  </p>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="color: #dc3545; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px;">Reason for blocking:</h3>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #555;">
      <%= blockReason || 'Policy violation detected' %>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #856404; margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px;">What happens next?</h4>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #856404;">
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your account access has been temporarily suspended</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">You will not be able to login or access your seller dashboard</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Your existing listings are currently hidden from buyers</li>
      <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">No new orders will be processed</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="border: 1px solid #d1ecf1; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #d1ecf1; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
    <h4 style="color: #0c5460; margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px;">How to resolve this:</h4>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #0c5460; font-size: 14px;">
      If you believe this blocking was made in error or if you have resolved the issue mentioned above, 
      please contact our support team immediately. We will review your case and may reinstate your account 
      once the matter is resolved.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="mailto:support@canadianbazaar.ca" 
       style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
      Contact Support
    </a>
  </div>

  <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    We appreciate your understanding and look forward to resolving this matter quickly.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>Canadian Bazaar Admin Team</strong>
  </p>
</div>